				</a>
				<a href="https://facebook.com/deskbly" target="_blank" rel="noopener" aria-label="Facebook">
					<svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M24 12.073c0-6.627-5.373-12-12-12s-12 5.373-12 12c0 5.99 4.388 10.954 10.125 11.854v-8.385H7.078v-3.47h3.047V9.43c0-3.007 1.792-4.669 4.533-4.669 1.312 0 2.686.235 2.686.235v2.953H15.83c-1.491 0-1.956.925-1.956 1.874v2.25h3.328l-.532 3.47h-2.796v8.385C19.612 23.027 24 18.062 24 12.073z"/></svg>
				</a>
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="footer-col">
			<h4>Categories</h4>
			<ul>
				<li><a href="/category/desks">Desks</a></li>
				<li><a href="/category/chairs">Chairs</a></li>
				<li><a href="/category/accessories">Accessories</a></li>
			</ul>
		</div>
		<div class="footer-col">
			<h4>Company</h4>
			<ul>
				<li><a href="/about">About Us</a></li>
				<li><a href="/contact">Contact</a></li>
				<li><a href="/privacy-policy">Privacy Policy</a></li>
				<li><a href="/affiliate-disclosure">Affiliate Disclosure</a></li>
			</ul>
		</div>
	</div>
	<div class="footer-bottom">
		<p>&copy; {today.getFullYear()} Deskbly. All rights reserved.</p>
	</div>
</footer>

<style>
	footer {
		background: rgb(var(--gray-dark));
		color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
		padding: 3em 1em 1.5em;
		margin-top: 4em;
	}
	.footer-grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: 2fr 1fr 1fr;
		gap: 2em;
		max-width: 960px;
		margin: 0 auto;
	}
	.footer-col h4 {
		color: white;
		margin-bottom: 0.8em;
		font-size: 1em;
	}
	.footer-col p {
		font-size: 0.85em;
		line-height: 1.6;
		margin: 0 0 1em 0;
	}
	.footer-col ul {
		list-style: none;
		padding: 0;
		margin: 0;
	}
	.footer-col ul li {
		margin-bottom: 0.4em;
	}
	.footer-col ul a {
		color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
		text-decoration: none;
		font-size: 0.85em;
	}
	.footer-col ul a:hover {
		color: white;
	}
	.social-icons {
		display: flex;
		gap: 0.8em;
	}
	.social-icons a {
		color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);
		transition: color 0.2s;
	}
	.social-icons a:hover {
		color: white;
	}
	.footer-bottom {
		max-width: 960px;
		margin: 2em auto 0;
		padding-top: 1.5em;
		border-top: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.15);
		text-align: center;
		font-size: 0.8em;
	}
	@media (max-width: 720px) {
		.footer-grid {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
			gap: 1.5em;
		}
	}
</style>
